Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:06.47,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Once, when I was little, I saw God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:11.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It was then, for the first time, that I learned the reason for which I drew...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:15.74,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I wondered what I would do if I couldn't draw anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.94,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ah, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:22.94,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If I were ever to stop drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:26.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,at that moment I will return my life to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:33.24,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}watashi ga umareta asa no machi yuki no naka ni umoreta
