Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:45.41,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:50.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:56.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:58.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
