Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:08.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:13.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:20.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:26.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:32.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:44.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:55.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:33.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:38.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:45.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:50.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:56.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:58.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:02.70,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:08.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:13.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:20.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:26.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:32.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:44.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:55.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:04.03,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I didn't even notice what was about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:12.34,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, she was right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.31,thoughts,,0,0,0,,By my side, as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.17,clover,,0,0,0,,I finished just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I finished it just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.00,clover,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.91,clover,,0,0,0,,It looks simple from afar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.88,clover,,0,0,0,,...but you realize how intricate the design is when you come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.79,clover,,0,0,0,,It's complicated yet serene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.97,clover,,0,0,0,,It's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:57.72,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Takemoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I just feel so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean... I don't get praised very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan, I think I'm going to become a restoration worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Restoration worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:19.09,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm going to travel around the country, restoring temples and shrines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:24.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Most older architectures don't have any blueprints left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:31.37,clover,,0,0,0,,...so you need to look at actual parts from each building and analyze how they were built.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.69,clover,,0,0,0,,It looks like I have a soft spot for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:41.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I get absorbed in it... or rather, I get obsessed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't know how else to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:51.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Once this Hamabi Festival is over, I bet graduation will come in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't that hard to imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun will be somewhere in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.73,clover,,0,0,0,,...Ayu will be in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.69,clover,,0,0,0,,...and I'll be in Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.69,clover,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to see each other so easily anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.85,clover,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to ask, "What do you want for lunch?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Or to go to the Maruei Bakery together to buy snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Everything we did together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.58,clover,,0,0,0,,We can't casually spend our days together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you really returning to Nagano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:36.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan, why won't you tell Sensei your true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.87,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:54.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun, what's the significance of the path that I have to choose at the expense of someone else's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:05:00.56,clover,,0,0,0,,What can I give Shuu-chan in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:08.36,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, Shuu-chan will probably tell me that he'll sacrifice everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:10.40,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the matter, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:18.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Were you up all night preparing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.62,clover,,0,0,0,,No, I just woke up early, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.62,clover,,0,0,0,,I had nothing else to do, so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.29,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the first day of the Hamabi Festival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:32.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei, could it be that you are feeling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.99,clover,,0,0,0,,No, I was just thinking that the festivities are coming to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.71,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.60,clover,,0,0,0,,We still have three more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.50,clover,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.98,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There is one hour left until opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:51.63,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Students whose works are not in position yet, please have them ready by 9:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Are you really returning to Nagano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, cart coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what a strong wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm getting pushed by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't move your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.50,clover,,0,0,0,,It's so windy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.71,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the displays outside will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Look, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.70,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if a storm is coming?
