Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:42.14,clover,,0,0,0,,Good morning, useless guard dog with his fledgling eggshell still stuck to his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:46.72,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(529,151)\fnFormal436 BT\3c&H8671A0&\c&HD2ABFF&\fad(237,0)}Speaking Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:46.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Good morning, nice guy with that unnatural growth on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.69,clover,,0,0,0,,How are things going, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:53.14,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Based on that pathetic look on your face, it looks like Rika hasn't let you into her bedroom yet, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.43,clover,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you like this, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.31,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can switch anytime with me, the nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.31,clover,,0,0,0,,You've been looking healthier lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.53,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa, you're laying it on thick again this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.17,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was thinking only your eyebrows were thick, but your chest hair and beard are also extra thick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.80,clover,,0,0,0,,It must be thanks to that boy from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.66,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I mean, why the heck wasn't your head blessed with the same thick hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.75,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What did you say? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.75,clover,,0,0,0,,It might be thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Things have become much easier since he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.97,clover,,0,0,0,,He easily befriended Carlos, who's so difficult sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:22.49,clover,,0,0,0,,It seems the two of them go out drinking and have a blast every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I've slept so well at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:29.49,clover,,0,0,0,,I haven't slept this well since I came to Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:32.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Really, aren't you glad those two get along so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, fledgling! Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go back to your kingdom of hair follicles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Dammit, that bastard with the suspicious head...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.00,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll expose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.45,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely expose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.79,clover,,0,0,0,,She locked me out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Man, what a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:09:03.04,clover,,0,0,0,,She said "two-bedroom", so I figured it would be one room with two beds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.80,clover,,0,0,0,,But to think that there are two bedrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.40,clover,,0,0,0,,It's so cruel. On top of that, the rooms have locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.94,clover,,0,0,0,,This is a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:19.25,clover,,0,0,0,,But locks, y'know... are for opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:26.81,clover,,0,0,0,,But... If I force my way in, the door to her heart might be sealed shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:32.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Well... you need to take your time... and work carefully... on things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.03,clover,,0,0,0,,The cactus that Mayama left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Could it be that something happened to Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:48.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps it received a transmission of impure thoughts from its owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.23,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Rika is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.89,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.50,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Someone go get the executive committee! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.72,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Someone's been hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:01.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei, there's something going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, Hanamoto speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I heard a glass panel that they were moving shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.90,clover,,0,0,0,,I heard a girl was caught underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.10,clover,,0,0,0,,I saw her. It was a small girl with long hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.50,clover,,0,0,0,,She was covered in blood and glass shards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.39,clover,,0,0,0,,She had a big gash on her head...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard the girl is a senior oil painting major.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.81,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:33.77,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.82,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.35,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Tell me it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.06,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.11,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Don't cut your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please go get a cart. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.50,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring some water in a bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Oh, and bring a broom and a deck brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.15,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It was Hanamoto-san from the oil painting department.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.83,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You know, Hanamoto-sensei's cousin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,We're about to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry up, this is a passageway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hey, get a bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.19,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.31,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Tell me it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.48,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:14.88,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.31,thoughts,,0,0,0,,..she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:21.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But she was right in front of me just a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:23.72,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan's been hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.08,clover,,0,0,0,,And Sensei rode with her in the ambulance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:36.36,clover,,0,0,0,,He said he'll contact you on your cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.96,clover,,0,0,0,,...and for us to stay at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.83,clover,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.51,clover,,0,0,0,,So... Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.54,clover,,0,0,0,,If Sensei calls you, please let me know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.99,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ah... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.76,clover,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.35,clover,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:50.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.14,clover,,0,0,0,,...right hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:06.71,clover,,0,0,0,,After that, Yamada-san and I helped pick up the glass shards and wash away the blood that had pooled on the asphalt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.09,clover,,0,0,0,,The blood of the girl I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.51,clover,,0,0,0,,President, I'd like to make a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:24.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Our sales in the second half of the year increased 12-15% in every department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Either way, these seem to be very good figures for this time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:33.31,clover,,0,0,0,,However, profits are down slightly at the North American plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Can't we fix that by cutting personnel costs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.28,clover,,0,0,0,,We don't need 120 workers at that plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.55,clover,,0,0,0,,President, excuse me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:48.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Cutting the workforce and increasing individual work hours will improve cost performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Is my view mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Only idiots cut experienced workers these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:02.28,clover,,0,0,0,,People without a vision of what's to come in the next ten years sure do things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.61,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for intruding on your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.88,clover,,0,0,0,,We've come to deliver a birthday present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.87,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.93,clover,,0,0,0,,My birthday is in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:27.15,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What in the world is this cheap and poorly designed work outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.07,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it? It's a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:33.76,clover,,0,0,0,,After all, today marks the day when you return to square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.20,clover,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I looked into your family history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:41.69,clover,,0,0,0,,I hear that your father, the founder of this company, was a wonderful technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.08,clover,,0,0,0,,But you, the second generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Although you started as a technician like your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.26,clover,,0,0,0,,...you forgot the joy of building things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:54.97,clover,,0,0,0,,...and used both people and money like pawns in the name of profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:59.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I can't let my father's legacy stay with a company like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.94,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm taking all of it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.30,clover,,0,0,0,,All of it, along with your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Starting today, we're the new board of directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:11.21,clover,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd make it in time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:15.73,clover,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd hit retirement and end up spending the rest of my life in Chicago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.91,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to make you wait, Uncle Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.78,clover,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me that you bought out my company's stocks and took over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:27.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Lucas Digital Arts owns 35% of our shares!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.37,clover,,0,0,0,,If so, then how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Um... these...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.86,clover,,0,0,0,,I got these from Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.93,clover,,0,0,0,,He was saying, "We only have XLs, but please wear them if you like."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:46.35,sign,,0,0,0,,Peter Lucas Digital Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:44.53,clover,,0,0,0,,"He's gonna go bankrupt and won't have anything to wear, so please take this to him."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.95,clover,,0,0,0,,So he sent a hundred of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.42,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.31,clover,,0,0,0,,What did I ever did to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:52.76,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you stand to gain from doing something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.56,clover,,0,0,0,,What about my position? And my family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.70,clover,,0,0,0,,We had a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.86,clover,,0,0,0,,We all had one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.18,clover,,0,0,0,,And... these boys as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.66,clover,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.32,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.31,clover,,0,0,0,,What about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that I did something to deserve your grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.72,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:22.55,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's my job to curse and hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.67,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So you two should move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.23,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Got it? Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.86,clover,,0,0,0,,When did this happen anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.77,clover,,0,0,0,,We bought out that Japanese corporation over a decade ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Why now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.19,clover,,0,0,0,,You're telling me that you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:46.12,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't really care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:51.44,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right, you should go look for a new home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.04,clover,,0,0,0,,That mansion of yours belongs to the company, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.63,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:03.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we're going to file a bunch of lawsuits, so make sure you have a lot of cash ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.31,clover,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:10.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and about your son and your grandchildren...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Leave them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.65,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with them to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.15,clover,,0,0,0,,They should come seeking revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Just like we did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.74,clover,,0,0,0,,They can prepare for decades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.83,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll take them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.86,clover,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.41,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Now, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:41.19,thoughts,,0,0,0,,When you shine light on it, it heads towards the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's the smallest robot in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Its name is "Kabu-tan".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Kaoru's "Ka" and Shinobu's "Bu".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called "Kabu-tan".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.61,clover,,0,0,0,,This is only the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.77,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll hunt you down until you can't find a moment's rest in your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.29,clover,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:13.29,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna corner you until you wish you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.91,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.47,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.21,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I couldn't keep my promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:28.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.62,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I couldn't protect what was precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:46.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Gusts of wind blew through the afternoon of the festival's first day, which became quite dreary with sprinkling rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:59.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Crowds of people gathered all day before Hagu-chan's painting of golden gingko trees lined up beneath the endless blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.86,clover,,0,0,0,,No word came from Sensei for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:13.14,clover,,0,0,0,,It was finally evening, when the wind had died down and it had become dark outside, when my cellphone rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:20.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan's injuries required ten stitches on her head and thirteen stitches on her right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:28.68,clover,,0,0,0,,The worst of her injuries was on her right hand, and over six hours were needed to operate on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Ayu... Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan, these... I brought things that I thought you might need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.84,clover,,0,0,0,,How is it? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:48.32,clover,,0,0,0,,It's starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:53.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Especially my head. I wonder if it's because the anesthesia is starting to wear off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.14,clover,,0,0,0,,And your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:00.46,clover,,0,0,0,,My hand... doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.07,clover,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any broken bones either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.65,clover,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you two came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:16.33,clover,,0,0,0,,I brought some things that she might need... Like a change of clothes and towels...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, great. You're a lifesaver, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:25.65,clover,,0,0,0,,She's still on medication, so we should let her rest some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.85,clover,,0,0,0,,You two should go home and sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.29,clover,,0,0,0,,There are still two more days of the Hamabi Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.30,clover,,0,0,0,,You two haven't gotten much sleep, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.75,clover,,0,0,0,,But Sensei... we still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:44.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun, let's leave things to Sensei for now. We should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Bye then, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything that the doctor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:17.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Please. I'm afraid of not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:23.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Your wounds runs from the base of your fingers across your palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.96,clover,,0,0,0,,The tendons were severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:30.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Today's surgery was to reconnect the blood vessels, tendons, and nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Your stitches should come out in about ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:38.88,clover,,0,0,0,,The problem is the nerves that are concentrated at the base of your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:43.49,clover,,0,0,0,,They can fuse upon healing and result in secondary damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:50.69,clover,,0,0,0,,In order to avoid that, you'll have to be hospitalized for over two months and partake in intensive rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:55.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan... I knew something was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.97,clover,,0,0,0,,My right hand doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.23,clover,,0,0,0,,It's because the nerves were cut, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:08.19,clover,,0,0,0,,It would've have been better if my hand hurt right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:15.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Her voice that undoubtedly wanted to ask, "Will it get better?" broke off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.08,clover,,0,0,0,,As if it was crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:29.73,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:29.73,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:40.19,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:40.19,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.61,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.61,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:52.74,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:52.74,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:22:06.22,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:22:06.22,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.96,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.96,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.82,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.82,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:16.16,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:16.16,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:24.86,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:24.86,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:28.26,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:28.26,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:34.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Pondering my inabilities.
